    <div data-cid="1929392">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1929392">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/moccy/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img9.doubanio.com/icon/u1476643-5.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/moccy/" class="name">猫薄荷</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2009-03-27" class="main-meta">2009-03-27 13:46:52</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1929392/">分镜高手的华丽悲剧</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1929392_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1929392">
                    <div class="short-content">

                           喜欢漫画的都有点二次元中毒，尤其是打小看着CLAMP的。毫无疑问，她们善于运用网点，一部《X》简直就是部网点运用的教程；她们更善于分镜：我们就这样在《CLOVER》里面看着素轻盈的落下，脚尖缓缓触地，宛如天使。过了很久很久以后，偶尔想到时，那一格格分镜就像烙进心里，...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1929392-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1929392_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1929392_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1929392" title="有用">
